Mythomagic. Percy Jackson fandom. Digital card game.

This is an unofficial, fan-made card game inspired by mythology. It is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by Rick Riordan, Disney-Hyperion, or any other rights holder. All trademarks, characters, and related intellectual property from the Percy Jackson & the Olympians series and associated works are the property of their respective owners. This project is created solely for non-commercial, fan-use purposes.
